  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    If you are considering using a&amp;nbsp;spreadsheet to track your project's backlog and burndown consider these two&#xD;
    templates&amp;nbsp;kindly provided by Clay Ver Valen and Petri Heiramo.&amp;nbsp; Both templates are excellent and one is sure&#xD;
    to be appeal to your project. Petri's template uses macros which provide a richer functionality but may be an&#xD;
    impediment to some.&amp;nbsp; Petris' template is pre-loaded with sample data while Clay provides a separate sample for his&#xD;
    template.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    如果你正在考虑使用电子表格来跟踪你的项目订单和燃尽图，可以使用下面由Clay Ver Valen和Petri&#xD;
    Heiramo提供的两个模板。这两个模板都很优秀，相信一定有一个适合你的项目。Petri的模板使用Excel宏提供了更丰富的功能,但对某些人来说可能是一个障碍。Petris的模板中提供了样例数据，而Clay的模板中也提供了自己的样例数据。&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
